All Packages

Package Summary
Package
Description
day
This package contains classes that define each day of the game - Battle.java, Day.java, and Shop.java
exceptions
This package contains custom exceptions.
generators
This package contains generators to randomly generate an Item or a Monster.
generators.registries
This package contains the available Monsters and Items that can be randomly generated.
gui
This package contains the GameEnvironment, and all the GUI classes.
gui.customElements
This package contains custom elements for the GUI classes.
interfaces
This package contains an interface for classes that contain images.
leaderboard
This package contains the class and text file associated with the local leaderboard.
player
This package contains information that is unique to the player - classes Inventory, Player, PlayerScore and Team.
purchasable
The Purchasable package contains all the classes that can be bought from the Stores.
purchasable.items
The Item package containing all the various item types and functionality.
purchasable.items.armors
The Armor package which contains the different Armor items.
purchasable.items.food
The Food package which contains the different types of Food items.
purchasable.items.weapons
The Weapons package containing the different types of weapons.
purchasable.monsters
Monster package containing the different Monster classes.
random_event
Random Events package containing all the logic for running random events.
test
This package contains all the unit tests relating to the functionality of the game.
